{"tid":1483794,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我地籌錢整把[光復香港 時代革命]雨傘 落雨發夢都幾壯觀下","createTime":"2019-08-18T13:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:06:57.000Z","uid":6489,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43808aea05bfe8d8f1c9598c3f1c830310a218ba","tid":1483794,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"話說今日去維園路上落大雨塞緊既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到個個開哂摭 如果我地籌錢做翻把<br />\n<br />\n每個香港人發夢岀街個陣<br />\n<br />\n都有一把上面寫住［光復香港 時代革命］都幾壯觀<br />\n<br />\n由上面望上去 甚至乎比世界所有記者見到 都可以做一個流動宣傳<br />\n<br />\n我只係有呢個idea 唔知咁多位buy唔buy 如果要其他巴打幫手由設計去到眾籌至岀品 會唔會可行?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862c0927ff05984c8322ac7a0f28bf60dbf06cd2","tid":1483794,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"由上面望上去<br />\n咁啲字唔會細到睇唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6596c86bb889a6d3b23b8437e8c47668f0138196","tid":1483794,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d9867cb242b7c8a55f67a5093dbf876567daab","tid":1483794,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"862c0927ff05984c8322ac7a0f28bf60dbf06cd2","tid":1483794,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"由上面望上去<br />\n咁啲字唔會細到睇唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2